Spectra (1st row, A) and spectrogram (2nd row, B) of the calling song of 
<taxonomicName box="[1036,1283,1474,1496]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Platylomia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="142" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shaanxiensis" status="sp. n.">
